-- Iren Is Planning to Invest in Water-Supply Companies, la Repubblica Says
-- Steve Scherer
-- 2010-09-20T06:06:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/iren-is-planning-to-invest-in-water-supply-companies-la-repubblica-says.html

          
          
             Iren SpA, a municipal electricity
producer, plans to buy companies that supply water and will
include its strategy in a new industrial plan to be drafted in
December, la Repubblica reported, without citing anyone.  
 Acque Potabili SpA may be one of the companies Iren will
seek to purchase, the newspaper said.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
